import Page from "../common/Page"; import classes from "./ProfilePage.module.css"; import {useState, useEffect, useContext} from "react" import {getCurrentUser} from '../../../api/UserApi' import AuthContext from '../../../store/auth-context'; const ProfilePage = () => { const [user, setUser] = useState({}) const authCtx = useContext(AuthContext) useEffect(() => { if(authCtx.isLoggedIn){ getCurrentUser(authCtx.token) .then((data) => { setUser(data); }) .catch((err) => { alert(err.message); }); } }, [authCtx]) return (

{user.username}

Name : Bruce Wayne
Email : {user.email}
Address : {user.address}
Phone : {user.phone}
Balance : {user.balance}
Skill :

SOCIAL MEDIA

: Bruce Wayne
: rentup@gmail.com
: 221B Baker Street
: Punching the bad guys
); }; export default ProfilePage;
